rosoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	4、如果越狱过程中某个进程被卡住，那就放心的重启你的设备，不会对越狱造成任何影响。</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	5、<strong>本工具仅适应于iOS7 - 7.0.4系统，大家还应确保自己的系统不是由OTA升级而来</strong>（若是，请备份系统并完整恢复一次）。</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	<span style=\\\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\\\">iOS7.x完美越狱工具v1.0.1下载</span>：Windows版&nbsp; ||&nbsp;&nbsp;Mac版</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	越狱教程：</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	1、将设备连接到电脑，若iTunes自动启动并试图连接设备请将其关闭，然后我们来运行evasi0n7越狱工具：</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	<img data-pinit=\\\"registered\\\" src=\\\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2013/12/20131225_122947_844.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 600px;\\\" /></p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	2、在evasi0n7识别出设备型号后，请点击Jailbreak开始越狱。然后大家就可以嗑瓜子围观了，几分钟就可以完成所有步骤的。</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(39, 42, 48); font-family:  Microsoft Yahei ; \\\">\\r\\n	<img data-pinit=\\\"registered\\\" src=\\\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2013/12/20131225_122951_692.jpg\\\" style=\\\"bord